Subject: Codex LM Studio Capture Directory

Description: Marker for captured LM Studio manager outputs and OpenAI Codex worker returns.

@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\CodexLMStudioOrchestrationWorkspace.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\workspaces\codex_lmstudio_orchestrator\Queue.sop

& [CodexLMStudioCaptureDirectory] is the capture surface for the orchestration workspace
  + [capture_root] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\workspaces\codex_lmstudio_orchestrator\captures
  + [capture_status] is initialized
  + [capture_use] is store raw LM Studio manager output, OpenAI Codex worker output, validation reports, and blocked notes before integration
  + [first_expected_capture] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\workspaces\codex_lmstudio_orchestrator\captures\codex_lmstudio_manager_dry_run_001_output.sop
  + [capture_outside] is secrets, auth files, unredacted credentials, unrelated project output, and hidden state claims

  = must: capture raw outputs before validation or integration
  = must: keep rejected output as evidence when a retry is needed
  = must: redact credentials before any capture is committed
  - never: treat a capture file as authority until Codex records integration disposition
